 
<p>

The Biden administration told US pharmacies that refusing to fill a
prescription because the patient is pregnant <a href="https://www.cnn.com/2022/07/13/health/biden-abortion-pharmacy-guidance/index.html">violates federal
anti discrimination law</a>.
<p>
This rule interpretation can <a href="https://www.latimes.com/california/story/2022-07-11/post-roe-many-autoimmune-patients-lose-access-to-gold-standard-drug">protect their access to medicine</a> for
treating various diseases including lupus,
as well as protecting access to some methods of abortion.
<p>
I expect that the fanatical justices will look for an way to overturn
it.
<p>
Meanwhile, in Texas, doctors already hesitate just as <a href="https://stallman.org/archives/2022-may-aug.html#5_July_2022_(poland_abortion_law_izabela_sajbor)">Izabela Sajbor's</a>
doctors in Poland hesitated, with fatal results in her case.

 